---
title: Tex-Mex Chicken Traybake & Cheesy Potatoes with Charred Corn Salad & Chipotle Yoghurt
description: These cheesy potato chunks are going to make you weak at the knees! Serve them up with thick and juicy slices of Tex-Mex spiced chicken, fresh tomato and charred corn salsa for a lip-smackingly good family dinner.
